{"tid":2303846,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情被逼分隔異地 移民爸爸為工作先赴加國 兒子誤會被遺棄","createTime":"2020-11-28T09:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T10:26:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6250879bfe39cc9e6fc9dd2c0c76758ca44ed704","tid":2303846,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"香港環境急劇轉變，不少人萌生移民念頭，尤其有下一代的家庭，為子女着想，都會選擇離港尋找安樂窩。Winda一家四口自去年社會運動爆發後，已部署送兩位兒子去加拿大升學，由於丈夫Jason的工作簽證批核順利，所以今年6月已先行出發，而兩位兒子因疫情拖延至今都未獲准入境，一家四口被逼分隔異地大半年，兒子甚至誤以為被爸爸遺棄在香港。<br />\n<br />\n「初時大仔真的接受不到，問我為甚麼爸爸貿然走了，剩下我們三個在香港做甚麼？他真的嬲了爸爸，FaceTime都不願見，拿電話給他，他都擰轉面走人。」Winda說這事令她和丈夫很頭痛，但無奈疫情打亂了他們的移民計劃。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201128/GDZCHLQUFZB75O7BWZOI7ILPKI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201128%2FGDZCHLQUFZB75O7BWZOI7ILPKI%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7ClSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=7815f6fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201128%2FGDZCHLQUFZB75O7BWZOI7ILPKI%2F&h=14b758cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201128/GDZCHLQUFZB75O7BWZOI7ILPKI/</a>"},{"pid":"411a9c46bcfa4cc9ad16bcc7b2e98cada1f371e2","tid":2303846,"uid":72009,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"小朋友第時會多謝老豆，現在係on 9 d"},{"pid":"fa9d2640ba7eb28e8549a37516d3ec8cecc31479","tid":2303846,"uid":264158,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:19:40.000Z","msg":"雖然係有啲波折 但可以移到加拿大 好多人都好羨慕佢哋啦"},{"pid":"e2c8a75c26a4aba21d65a3bab6ef6576e885ec5c","tid":2303846,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:26:13.000Z","msg":"忤逆仔！無老豆供書教學你遲啲就要戴紅領巾去中國讀習語錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}